        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThis is not compatible with Alpine, see https://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=aai/graphadmin.git;a=blob;f=src/main/docker/docker-entrypoint.sh;h=76c8d5e1309dfaa681be12781f168c1c170b4fb3;hb=refs/heads/master for an example of a way to do this in both ubuntu and alpine.  Thanks!",
