        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-08-28 13:59:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nhi James, \nThanks for the review. However, I am unsure of the reason of rejection. From what I can see the differences between my impl and reference link sent by you are as follows:\n\n1. UID for group and user  aaiadmin are different.\n2. The pre-processing is delegated in a seperate docker entrypoint script.\n3. In my case the user is added to sudo group.\n\nAny other point that I might have missed?\n\nI would be thankful to you if you could let me know the exact concern so that I could address the same soonest.\nThanks,\nRajeev",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
